text: Anzing is a municipality in the Upper Bavarian district of Ebersberg. ==Geography== ===Municipal divisions=== Constituent communities include Anzing, Auhofen, Boden, Froschkern, Frotzhofen, Garkofen, Hl. Kreuz, Höggerloh, Kaisersberg, Köppelmühle, Lindach, Mauerstetten, Obelfing, Oberasbach, Ranharting, Ried, Staudach, Unterasbach and Ziegelstadel. ==References== ==Other websites== *Community’s homepage *Sport club‘s homepage Category:Ebersberg (district)
